            "title": "內地對谷歌展開反壟斷調查",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地市監總局表示，谷歌公司涉嫌違反《中華人民共和國反壟斷法》，市場監管總局依法對谷歌開展立案調查。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250131_CH_Mexico_President2_source-ap.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250131_CH_Mexico_President2_source-ap.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市監總局公告中未有披露調查細節。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市監總局去年12月初亦曾經同樣以涉嫌違反反壟斷法為理由，對晶片製造商英偉達開展立案調查。</p>\n</div>",
